# Helm Charts

This directory contains Helm charts for deploying services to Kubernetes.

## Structure

- `service/` - Base Helm chart template for microservices
- Each service can override values using service-specific `values.yaml` files

## Deploying Services

Deploy services using Skaffold profiles:

```bash
# Deploy to local Kind cluster
skaffold run --profile=local

# Deploy to dev environment
skaffold run --profile=dev

# Deploy to production
skaffold run --profile=prod
```

## Manual Deployment

To manually deploy a service using Helm:

```bash
helm install <service-name> ./infra/helm/service \
  --set service.name=<service-name> \
  --set image.repository=<registry>/<service-name> \
  --set image.tag=<version> \
  --namespace=<namespace>
```

## Chart Development

To add a new Helm chart:

1. Create chart structure in this directory
2. Update `skaffold.yaml` to reference the chart
3. Configure values in deployment profiles

